<span class="item">
                        	<h1 class="fn">Sloppy Joes</h1>
</span>
                        	<div class="entry-meta">
								
                            	
                                	<p>Posted by Elise on Nov 10, 2009</p>
                            	
                            	<p>Filed under <a href="http://simplyrecipes.com/recipes/all_seasons/">All Seasons</a>, <a href="http://simplyrecipes.com/recipes/beef/">Beef</a>, <a href="http://simplyrecipes.com/recipes/comfort_food/">Comfort Food</a>, <a href="http://simplyrecipes.com/recipes/quick/">Quick</a>, <a href="http://simplyrecipes.com/recipes/sandwich/">Sandwich</a></p>
                            </div>
							
